data.description: WELCOME to your beautifully landscaped new HOME! As you step inside, the spacious foyer and open-concept living welcome you with an abundance of natural light and hard surface floors that grace the main level.    The living area seamlessly blends the living room, kitchen, and dining spaces, perfect for entertaining. The living room features a cozy fireplace, creating a comfortable and inviting ambiance. The kitchen is a chef's delight, with granite counters, a custom backsplash, and a kitchen island with seating. The large pantry ensures ample storage for all your culinary needs. A convenient powder room on the main level adds to the functionality of the space.    Heading upstairs, the primary bedroom awaits, complete with a tray ceiling that adds an elegant touch. The large closet provides plenty of storage space, and the private en suite bath boasts a dual vanity, a separate tub, and a shower, creating a luxurious retreat. The well-appointed secondary bedrooms are comfortable and accommodating, and an additional full bath serves these bedrooms and guests. The upstairs laundry room offers convenience and ease.    Step outside to the large fenced backyard and patio, providing a wonderful space for outdoor activities and relaxation. The attached 2-car garage completes this home, offering both parking and storage.    This home combines comfort and style in a well-thought-out layout. Don't miss the chance to make it yours and enjoy the convenience of modern living combined with outdoor enjoyment. Come and experience the lifestyle this home has to offer!
